             was indicted for <rs id="t18291029-213-off1208" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291029-213-off1208" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291029-213-off1208" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291029-213-cd1209" type="crimeDate">6th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291029-213-off1208 t18291029-213-cd1209"></join>, 6 knives, value 6s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18291029-213-victim1763" type="victimName">
                     Thomas 
                     Saunders
                  <interp inst="t18291029-213-victim1763" type="surname" value="Saunders"></interp>
